description:
Is Hollywood’s fascination with spirits, demons, and witchcraft a big joke? Or is Hollywood the place of Satan’s throne? Matthew Schanche and MacKenzie Drebit interview Scott Mayer whose ministry, Little Light Studios, exposes Satan’s tactics in the entertainment industry and shows why spiritualism in entertainment is no laughing matter. In this episode we reveal the shocking extent of Satan’s influence through media.

Get ready for the truth about how Satan is using The Chosen, Jesus Revolution, and the Asbury revival to meet his goals. Discover how Christian movies and entertainment are being used to warp our views of Christ and to prepare the world for the fulfillment of Bible prophecy. This episode has a compelling message for all Christian youth, and especially for those interested in the media arts.

6:08 Scott: Young Adventists in media arts.

10:25 Scott: What Hollywood is really like. How he lost his way.

13:01 Scott: Letting God make the decisions.

17:58 Matt: Worldly success and stories of broken souls.

25:05 Scott: Conversion experience. .
31:28 MacKenzie: The 5th dimension.

35:15 Scott: What entertainment is. Word study.
36:04 Matt and Scott: The spiritualism of the elite. Contrast between God’s and Satan’s offers.

51:48 Matt: Jesus revival vs satanic entertainment. Satan’s strategy in playing both sides.
53:15 Scott: Counterfeit trinities, baby saviors.
57:25 Matt: Satan’s Jesus knockoffs. Jesuit theatre. 
59:32 Scott: Erosion of truth and objective reality. Reflections on The Chosen. Why it’s alarming.

1:06:41 Scott: The Chosen’s Catholic consultant on the set to ensure Catholic principles are correctly portrayed. The Chosen as a means of fulfilling prophecy.
1:07:38 MacKenzie: Jonathon Roumie, Roman Catholic and Knights Templar.
1:08:26 Matt: Freemasonry and Los Angeles. 
1:18:05 Scott: Answer to question, Why are you shoving your religion down my throat? 
1:19:10 MacKenzie: It’s all about worship in the end. Satan’s purpose. 
1:21:10 Matt: Freemasonry worship principles. 
1:24:54 Matt: Architectural evidence of Hollywood’s Luciferian connections.
1:29:25 MacKenzie: The Chosen ideology, indoctrinating viewers on the wrong Jesus.
1:35:46 Scott: Musicians discussing “this Jesus,” “this version of Jesus.”
1:36:55 Jesus Revolution
1:40:10 Matt: Devaluing Christ’s sacrifice. Discussion on legalism.
1:42:49 MacKenzie: The Family.

1:49:25 Matt: What we’re expecting to see is a false revival. 
1:50:25 MacKenzie: Latter rain is coming. Asbury revival. 
1:54:49 Scott: What makes a real Christian. Hearers and doers. 
1:57:15 MacKenzie: Satan as an angel of light. Scott relates a story about Asbury. 
2:01:50 MacKenzie: Demonic presence, Satan’s realm is very real. 
2:07:20 Scott: Importance of investigating prophecy.
2:09:46 MacKenzie: Defining spiritualism. The big lie.
2:10:36 Scott: Foundations of technology. Spiritualism, seances.
2:15:01 Scott: The essence of spiritualism. Connections between modern media and witchcraft.
2:16:49 Matt: The rainmaker. Scott: The rain man.
2:21:47 Matt: The battle is real. We’re the object of this war. 
2:23:14 MacKenzie: In entertainment, who’s connected to darkness, who’s not? 
2:29:17 Matt: How can we help people discern between the real and fake? 
2:30:52 MacKenzie: Danger of Christians getting “addicted” to sermons, presentations. 
2:34:34 Matt: Possessed actors. Method acting vs having the character of God. 
2:40:05 Role of Disney in promoting spiritualism, witchcraft. 
2:47:53 Scott: Pixar’s new movie Elemental.
2:51:00 Disney and the Jesuits. 
2:55:58 Matt’s closing remarks. Grateful God has pulled us out of the dark.
2:57:09 Scott: Principles to recognize what God is asking you to do.
2:59:53 MacKenzie: Take-away. What to do now. Putting on Jesus.
3:01:17 Matt: Message to young people.
3:03:25 Scott’s closing message to youth.
3:04:11 MacKenzie: How you can serve God right now.
